* Home *

**Users**
Each registered user has a main directory.   When a user is registered their home page will be cloned from a template.

**Home**
The user is free to customize their home page and put any content that they wish.

**Installed apps**
When the user installs another Simple App it is added to their home page.  Installing an app typically clones many documents from the Template for that app.

**Security**
All pages are private to the owner.  The owner can choose to allow other specific people to view and modify their documents by editing the UserReaders or UserWriters.
